attributionInfo.agentName: Katie W., Stacey K. & Amy B.

data.description: This stunning, spacious, custom, brick home with elegant moldings and arched windows awaits you in highly sought after Radbourne! You’ll love the access to I-85, I-77, UNCC, shopping, restaurants, schools, parks, greenways (1 block away!) & comm. amenities. Updates: paint, hardwood floors, carpet, upstairs full bath, and luxurious kitchen cabinets, shelving, quartz countertops & seated island. Garage has a tech-tile floor, overhead electricity, TV mount. Entertainers dream- great parking, a vaulted foyer+dining combo (stunning centerpiece of the home & seats 14+), deck w/BBQ gas line, fabulous screened porch, fire/BBQ pit w/electric, eat-in kitchen opens to the family room w/gas fireplace. The formal living room w/French doors is also perfect for an office. Retreat to the grand primary suite w/sitting area, private screened porch, custom WIC, dual vanities, spa tub, & oversized shower. The 4th bed/bonus has a WIC & is wired for theater.
